===Etymology===
Chinese (Cantonese) [[雜碎]] (jaap6.sui3)
===Noun===
'''chop suey'''
#''(United States)'' a [[stir-fry]] vegetable dish, served with pieces of beef or pork in a semi-thick sauce, and often soy sauce
#''(Canada)'' steamed [[beansprout]]s served in a semi-thick sauce, and mixed with a choice of meat and/or vegetables

